WEBVTT

00:06:58.366 --> 00:07:00.378
you'll want to see some of that for yourself,

00:07:00.378 --> 00:07:02.086
so let me show you.

00:07:02.086 --> 00:07:03.403
Well first you need to work out

00:07:03.403 --> 00:07:05.441
where you want to set it up.

00:07:05.441 --> 00:07:07.418
Now, at this point you might be imagining

00:07:07.418 --> 00:07:10.936
one of those lovely tropical island tax havens

00:07:10.936 --> 00:07:12.941
but here's the thing,

00:07:12.941 --> 00:07:14.138
shockingly,

00:07:14.138 --> 00:07:16.482
my own hometown, London,

00:07:16.482 --> 00:07:17.811
and indeed the U.K.,

00:07:17.811 --> 00:07:20.533
is one of the best places in the world

00:07:20.533 --> 00:07:23.437
to set up an anonymous company.

00:07:23.437 --> 00:07:26.126
And the other, even better,

00:07:26.126 --> 00:07:30.049
I'm afraid that's America.